1. This project uses Yarn as the package manager.
2. The `common` folder contains shared types and utilities for both frontend and backend.
3. The `server` folder houses the backend implementation built with the @tarpit framework (https://github.com/isatiso/node-tarpit).
4. The `ui` folder contains the Angular-based frontend implementation.
5. The `deploy` folder is used for Docker image builds.
6. Use snake_case naming convention for all function and variable names.